    schema1:description "Anneliese Dodds was Minister for Development at the Foreign, Commonwealth and Development Office and Minister for Women and Equalities at the Department for Education from 8 July 2024 until 28 February 2025. She was elected as the MP for Oxford East in June 2017."@en ;
